{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Create a premium mobile-first interactive benefits section for Ariya Supplements’ sleep product, Calm Nights.The design should be inspired by premium wellness brands like Auri, using expandable accordion-style benefit cards.The section should feel clean, modern, trustworthy, and easy to scan on mobile devices.Use a white background, Ariya purple accents, rounded corners, subtle shadows, and generous spacing.Only one accordion should be expanded at a time. When tapped, the accordion should smoothly open to reveal additional information. When tapped again, it should collapse.SECTION HEADLINEWhy Calm Nights Feels DifferentSUPPORTING TEXTDesigned to help quiet a racing mind, support natural sleep, and help you wake up refreshed.ACCORDION 1Icon:
    BrainTitle:
    Quiets Racing ThoughtsIngredient Highlight:
    L-Theanine + Lemon BalmContent:
    L-Theanine and Lemon Balm help calm an overactive mind and ease the mental chatter that keeps many people awake at night.ACCORDION 2Icon:
    Lotus FlowerTitle:
    Supports Deep RelaxationIngredient Highlight:
    Chamomile + Magnolia BarkContent:
    Chamomile and Magnolia Bark help promote relaxation and support your body’s transition from a stressed state into a calmer one before bed.ACCORDION 3Icon:
    Crescent MoonTitle:
    Fall Asleep NaturallyIngredient Highlight:
    L-Tryptophan + Vitamin B6Content:
    L-Tryptophan helps support your body’s natural sleep pathways while Vitamin B6 helps support its utilization.ACCORDION 4Icon:
    ZZZ Sleep IconTitle:
    Stay Asleep LongerIngredient Highlight:
    Multi-Pathway FormulaContent:
    Calm Nights combines multiple ingredients that work together to support uninterrupted, restorative sleep throughout the night.ACCORDION 5Icon:
    SunriseTitle:
    Wake Up RefreshedIngredient Highlight:
    Melatonin-Free FormulaContent:
    Designed to support sleep without the next-day grogginess commonly associated with melatonin-based products.ACCORDION 6Icon:
    Magnifying GlassTitle:
    Built DifferentIngredient Highlight:
    Transparent Formula + Standardized ExtractsContent:
    No proprietary blends. Every ingredient and dosage is clearly listed, and our extracts are standardized for consistency and quality.ICON REQUIREMENTSUse these exact icons:Quiets Racing Thoughts → Brain IconSupports Deep Relaxation → Lotus Flower IconFall Asleep Naturally → Crescent Moon IconStay Asleep Longer → ZZZ Sleep IconWake Up Refreshed → Sunrise IconBuilt Different → Magnifying Glass IconDo not substitute other icons.Do not use abstract symbols.Do not use decorative illustrations.Icons should be:Small and premiumConsistent line-art styleAriya purplePositioned to the left of each accordion titleEasy to recognize instantlyDESIGN REQUIREMENTSMobile-first design.Use accordion cards similar to Auri’s benefits section.Only one accordion open at a time.Closed cards should remain compact and easy to scan.Use Ariya purple for active states, icons, and subtle accents.Keep background white.Use clean rounded corners and premium spacing.Benefit titles should be bold and easy to read.Ingredient highlights should appear directly underneath each benefit title in a smaller accent font.Maintain a luxury wellness aesthetic.Prioritize readability and user interaction.The section should help customers understand exactly how Calm Nights works in less than 10 seconds.The benefit flow should tell this story:Racing Thoughts → Relaxation → Fall Asleep → Stay Asleep → Wake Refreshed → Why Ariya Is Different, the symbol for quiets racing thoughts should be changed to a brain icon,  the symbol for supports deep relaxation should be changed to a leaf icon,  the symbol for stay asleep longer should be changed to a zzz icon,  the symbol for stay asleep longer should be changed to a stick mans head that is asleep with 2 letter z over the top of his head icon, the symbol for stay asleep longer should be changed to just the letter Z as the icon , can you add another Z next to the Z that is already there in the icon for stay asleep longer but make this new letter Z a little bit higher than the first one, Now add a 3rd and final Z next to the second Z on the icon for stay asleep longer and make that one a little bit higher than the second Z and also make sure none of them are touching all 3 of the Z should be close but not touching
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
  .ai-benefits-section-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.background_color }};
    padding: {{ block.settings.section_padding_mobile }}px 20px;
  }

  @media screen and (min-width: 750px) {
    .ai-benefits-section-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: {{ block.settings.section_padding_desktop }}px 40px;
      width: {{ block.settings.desktop_width_percent }}%;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
  }

  .ai-benefits-container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .ai-benefits-header-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .ai-benefits-headline-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.headline_size_mobile }}px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: {{ block.settings.headline_color }};
    margin: 0 0 12px 0;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  @media screen and (min-width: 750px) {
    .ai-benefits-headline-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.headline_size_desktop }}px;
    }
  }

  .ai-benefits-subtext-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.subtext_size }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.subtext_color }};
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .ai-benefits-accordion-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .ai-accordion-item-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.card_background }};
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.card_border_radius }}px;
    box-shadow: {{ block.settings.card_shadow }};
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .ai-accordion-header-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;
    padding: 20px;
    cursor: pointer;
    border: none;
    background: none;
    width: 100%;
    text-align: left;
    transition: background-color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .ai-accordion-header-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.card_hover_background }};
  }

  .ai-accordion-icon-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 32px;
    height: 32px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .ai-accordion-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 28px;
    height: 28px;
    color: {{ block.settings.icon_color }};
  }

  .ai-accordion-title-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    flex-grow: 1;
  }

  .ai-accordion-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.title_size }}px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: {{ block.settings.title_color }};
    margin: 0 0 4px 0;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .ai-accordion-ingredient-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.ingredient_size }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.ingredient_color }};
    margin: 0;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .ai-accordion-chevron-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    color: {{ block.settings.chevron_color }};
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .ai-accordion-item-{{ ai_gen_id }}.active .ai-accordion-chevron-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    transform: rotate(180deg);
  }

  .ai-accordion-content-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    max-height: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: max-height 0.3s ease, padding 0.3s ease;
  }

  .ai-accordion-item-{{ ai_gen_id }}.active .ai-accordion-content-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    max-height: 500px;
  }

  .ai-accordion-content-inner-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    padding: 0 20px 20px 68px;
  }

  .ai-accordion-text-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.content_size }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.content_color }};
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }
{% endstyle %}

